  <h2>What makes Hard mode hard</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>No outlines or geographic reference points</li>
    <li>Countries and territories appear in isolation</li>
    <li>Pure shape recognition, not deduction</li>
    <li>Fast feedback: your guess count tells the truth</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Scoring in Hard mode</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>Maximum score: <strong>2000 points</strong></li>
    <li>Wrong guess: <strong>−200 points</strong></li>
    <li>Time penalty: <strong>−10 points per second</strong></li>
  </ul>

  <p>
